title: EXPERIENCE THE MOTOR AND MOUNTAIN BEHIND FCA US ON CAMP JEEP® AND DRIVE FCA! AT THE 2015 ORANGE COUN
text:
9:00 a.m. Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015 Categories 
Events, Sports Experience Camp Jeep® and Drive FCA! at the 2015 Orange County International Auto Show for unique on and off-road fun with the Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep®, Ram Truck, and FIAT brands! Enter the 2015 $45,000 National Sweepstakes for a chance to win an FCA US vehicle from any one of the Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep, Ram Truck, FIAT or Alfa Romeo brands. Camp Jeep® – Professional 4x4 drivers steer OCIAS attendees in the latest Jeep brand vehicles, through an exciting outdoor off-road test track with logs, stumps, angled drive-overs, and a 35 degree angle mountain climb. Located in Lot 5. Available vehicles include: 2015 Jeep Grand Cherokee, 2015 Jeep Renegade Trailhawk, 2016 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited & 2016 Jeep Cherokee Trailhawk Drive FCA! – Register at tent behind Hall C to test drive the latest from FCA US including the all-new 2015 Jeep Renegade, a small sport-utility vehicle that offers a unique combination of best-in-class off-road capability, open air freedom and a segment-first nine-speed automatic transmission that contributes to outstanding driving dynamics on and off-road, as well as two fuel-efficient engines, and innovative safety and technology. Available vehicles include: 2015 Chrysler 200, 2015 Chrysler 300, 2015 Chrysler Town & Country, 2016 Jeep Cherokee, 2015 Jeep Grand Cherokee, 2015 Jeep Renegade, 2015 Dodge Challenger, 2015 Dodge Dart, 2015 Dodge Durango, 2015 Ram 1500, 2016 Fiat F00X & 2015 Fiat 500e Camp Jeep® Hours of Operation: Thursday, October 15 4:00 p.m. – 10:00 p.m. Friday, October 16 12:00 p.m. – 10:00 p.m. Saturday, October 17 9:00 a.m. – 10:00 p.m. Sunday, October 18 9:00 a.m. – 7:00 p.m. Drive FCA! Hours of Operation: Thursday, October 15 4:00 p.m. – 6:30 p.m. Friday, October 16 12:00 p.m. – 6:30 p.m. Saturday, October 17 9:00 a.m. – 6:30 p.m. Sunday, October 18 9:00 a.m. – 6:30 p.m. For product information and more visit www.FCANorthAmerica.com.
